 \Phi : H\to G\times G' \text{ given by } h \mapsto (\varphi(h), \varphi'(h)) 
 \pi_1 : G\times G' \to G \text{ and } \pi_2 : G\times G'\to G' 
 \varphi = \pi_1\circ \Phi, \text{ and } \varphi' = \pi_2\circ \Phi 
 \Phi(h) = (\varphi(h), \varphi'(h)) \quad\forall h\in H 
